'''Tineggizt''' d [[azzug]] i d-ileffun i [[tasga (tafekka)|tesga]] (tasga d izi i d-izzin i [[turin]]).<ref>[http://www.cedars-sinai.edu/Patients/Health-Conditions/Pleurisy.aspx Cedars-Sinai: Pleurisy.] {{Webarchive|url=https://web.archive.org/web/20171022025435/https://www.cedars-sinai.edu/Patients/Health-Conditions/Pleurisy.aspx |date=22 tuber 2017}}</ref> llan waṭas n yisragen d tmentilin iy zemren ad iglun s tneggizt maca ammusen invirusen (am tegnatin n [[igem|yigem]] anvirus) yettenfufuden seg turin ar umruj n tesga iga d aserag imezdi yakk s waṭas.<ref>[http://www.merckmanuals.com/home/lung_and_airway_disorders/pleural_disorders/viral_pleuritis.html The Merck Manual Home Health Handbook: Viral Pleuritis.] {{Webarchive|url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140903053313/http://www.merckmanuals.com/home/lung_and_airway_disorders/pleural_disorders/viral_pleuritis.html |date=03 ctember 2014}}</ref> Deg yal tikkelt anda ttihriwent turin i [[asgunef|wesgunef]] n [[azwu|wezwu]] yettili-d umrey gar n tissiwin n tsegwin yuzzgen.<ref>[http://www.wellmont.org/Health-And-Wellness/Health-Library/?eid=96798&lang=1033 Wellmont Health System: Pleurisy (pleuritis).] {{Webarchive|url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160318234822/http://wellmont.org/health-and-wellness/health-library/?eid=96798&lang=1033 |date=18 meɣres 2016}}</ref><ref>Marshall Cavendish Corporation. Encyclopedia of Health. Vol. 1-18. New York: Marshall Cavendish, 2010, Vol. 13, P. 831.</ref> anecta igellu-d s takma neɣ agaz (leqrḥ) anamsad deg tegnit n usgunef. Takma ayi d [[takma n yidmaren]] yeqqnen ɣer tneggizt.<ref>Light, Richard W., and Y. C. Gary Lee. Textbook of Pleural Diseases. London: Arnold, 2003.</ref>

== Isekna d yizmal ==
[[Asken]] amsekni n tneggizt d takma tamẓuwit tanamsadt d wefray s terɣi neɣ d takma fsusen deg tama tayeffust neɣ tazelmaṭ n [[idmaren|yidmaren]] deg wesgunef aladɣa deg temhelt n [[Azizzer|uzizzer]] d [[Asɣunef|usɣunef]].<ref>{{amnir n web | akala=http://thelungcenter.co.in/yahoo_site_admin/assets/docs/Understanding_Pleurisy.72202645.pdf | azwel=The Lung Center: Understanding Pleurisy | anefsar=The Lung Center, New Deli, India | amahil=An online information portal for the community | azmez n tuwwṭa =2013-06-22| akala n ufaylu = https://web.archive.org/web/20160303231648/http://thelungcenter.co.in/yahoo_site_admin/assets/docs/Understanding_Pleurisy.72202645.pdf | azmez n ufaylu = 3 meɣres 2016 }}</ref> Takma trennu deg usgunef alqayan, deg [[tusut]], deg [[anezzu|unezzu]] yakk d tadsa. Yerna takma n tneggizt tezmer ad teddu alamma d tuyat neɣ ar uzagur,<ref>[http://health.cvs.com/GetContent.aspx?token=f75979d3-9c7c-4b16-af56-3e122a3f19e3&chunkiid=96798 Beth Walsh, MA. Pleurisy (pleuritis).] {{Webarchive|url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170703040659/http://health.cvs.com/GetContent.aspx?token=f75979d3-9c7c-4b16-af56-3e122a3f19e3&chunkiid=96798 |date=03 yulyu 2017}}</ref>

S ugani ɣef umsisreg (ayen yellan d ssebba), Takma n yidmaren yeqqnen ar tneggizt tezmer ad iglu s kra n isekna am:<ref name="Pleurisy"/>
* Tusut takiwant
* [[Tawla]] d [[acittew|uqiccew]]
* Asgunef arurad
* Amray n usgunef
* Azzug deg ugerjum

